-----
SHA_PREPROCESSING
-----
bin/spatial SHA_PREPROCESSING --sim --vv


cd ~/spatial
bin/spatial SHA_PREPROCESSING --sim
./SHA_PREPROCESSING.sim ""

bin/spatial SHA_PREPROCESSING --synth --instrumentation --fpga=VCS
cd ./gen/SHA_PREPROCESSING
make > vcs.log
bash run.sh  > sha_pre_sim.log
cat sha_pre_sim.log
cd ~/spatial
rm -rf gen/SHA_PREPROCESSING

screen -S SHA_PREPROCESSING
bin/spatial SHA_PREPROCESSING --synth --instrumentation --fpga=zynq
cd gen/SHA_PREPROCESSING
make | tee make.log
cd verilog-zynq/
vim par_utilization.rpt
